org.apache.flink.graph.asm.dataset

接口 DataSetAnalytic<T,R>

  • 类型参数:
    T - element type
    R - the return type
    所有已知实现类:
    ChecksumHashCode, Collect, Count, DataSetAnalyticBase

    public interface DataSetAnalytic<T,R>
    A DataSetAnalytic is similar to a CustomUnaryOperation but is terminal and results are retrieved via accumulators. A Flink program has a single point of execution. A DataSetAnalytic defers execution to the user to allow composing multiple analytics and algorithms into a single program.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明

      Execute the program and return the result.

      Execute the program and return the result.
      R getResult()
      This method must be called after the program has executed. 1) "run" analytics and algorithms 2) call ExecutionEnvironment.execute() 3) get analytic results
      DataSetAnalytic<T,R> run(DataSet<T> input)
      All DataSetAnalytic processing must be terminated by an OutputFormat and obtained via accumulators rather than returned by a DataSet.
